reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This phone case fits my iPhone14 Promax perfectly. The color is a very subtle transparent pink. It makes the phone easier to grip. I put a pop socket on it to make it even easier to hold. The pop socket grips securely with no problem at all. This phone case is a great price for the quality and has protected my phone so far without any problems of overheating. The buttons and camera lens line up well with no issues. The case is lightweight and pliable yet very sturdy. It isn’t bulky whatsoever and easily fits in my scrubs pockets without falling out. I would definitely purchase this case again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this case, it has scratched in some spots....
reviews.reviewText: I really like this case! I got a cute pop socket to go with this case (I got purple) and I love it! the case is see through and the sides have scratched but you would not be able to tell. What I like about this case is that is it durable and it doesn't show signs of being dirty or being used. I have had this case for about 6 months now and most cases normally look a little worn at this point but I don't think that my case looks worn. The case is also sleek which I appreciate for how durable it is. I travel constantly and I need a durable case because I am always dropping my phone. I would like to get more colors because the case was reasonably priced and better looking than my typical otter box.
